1
00:00:01,440 --> 00:00:02,970
(Episode 56)

2
00:00:03,040 --> 00:00:04,540
He told his mom to head home first.

3
00:00:05,440 --> 00:00:08,680
Does this mean he's finally
going to make his move?

4
00:00:10,550 --> 00:00:12,950
Hong Ju, I have a favor to ask.

5
00:00:13,350 --> 00:00:14,390
A favor?

6
00:00:14,520 --> 00:00:17,290
I have some questions
about Director Ma's car accident,

7
00:00:17,620 --> 00:00:20,230
so could you set something up
with her for me?

8
00:00:21,330 --> 00:00:22,330
Me?

9
00:00:22,390 --> 00:00:25,430
If that's too much trouble,
you could just invite her to come here.

10
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:27,000
We could meet with her together.

11
00:00:28,130 --> 00:00:31,640
So you think Director Ma
looks like Oh Jang Mi?

12
00:00:32,070 --> 00:00:33,740
I saw her at the hotel reopening party.

13
00:00:34,370 --> 00:00:37,410
About the car accident and other things,
I wanted to ask her some questions.

14
00:00:39,310 --> 00:00:40,410
All right.

15
00:00:40,410 --> 00:00:42,010
If it's that important to you.

16
00:00:45,850 --> 00:00:48,820
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

17
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:56,530
What is it?
I'm busy, so just get to the point.

18
00:00:56,860 --> 00:00:58,230
It's about Kang Baek Ho.

19
00:00:59,060 --> 00:01:00,060
Who?

20
00:01:00,130 --> 00:01:03,870
I heard you and Baek Ho
met at the hotel reopening party.

21
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:05,800
The hotel reopening party?

22
00:01:05,900 --> 00:01:08,670
Baek Ho has some questions for you
about the car accident.

23
00:01:09,010 --> 00:01:11,380
He keeps saying you look
just like some other woman.

24
00:01:12,080 --> 00:01:13,610
So can you come over here now?

25
00:01:13,850 --> 00:01:14,850
What?

26
00:01:14,850 --> 00:01:17,480
Is Baek Ho there with Hong Ju?

27
00:01:18,780 --> 00:01:21,050
You haven't forgotten that you owe me,
have you?

28
00:01:21,550 --> 00:01:23,620
Of course not.

29
00:01:25,660 --> 00:01:28,360
But can I be the one to pick the place?

30
00:01:28,830 --> 00:01:30,330
Okay. I'll see you there, then.

31
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:33,700
What did she say? Is she coming?

32
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:37,170
Yes, but she wants to meet
at the hospital.

33
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,840
The hospital?

34
00:02:00,390 --> 00:02:01,460
What about Seo Rin?

35
00:02:02,230 --> 00:02:04,560
She was in a meeting with
General Manager Kang until a moment ago.

36
00:02:04,860 --> 00:02:05,860
I see.

37
00:02:06,130 --> 00:02:09,900
I'll know soon enough. I just have to go
and check on Oh Jang Mi.

38
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:13,070
- I'm going on ahead.
- Yes, ma'am.

39
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,480
CEO Chae.

40
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:34,590
Kang Baek Ho.

41
00:03:36,690 --> 00:03:37,690
CEO Chae?

42
00:03:44,230 --> 00:03:46,360
What brings you here, ma'am?

43
00:03:53,670 --> 00:03:57,210
I just met with Oh Jang Mi's doctor
to check on her condition.

44
00:03:57,540 --> 00:03:58,680
That's right.

45
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,180
I asked him to.

46
00:04:02,010 --> 00:04:05,920
It's only natural to be worried,
considering how much I cared for her.

47
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:08,920
You cared for Oh Jang Mi?

48
00:04:09,850 --> 00:04:11,520
What are you doing here, Team Leader Jin?

49
00:04:12,060 --> 00:04:14,890
And with Lawyer Kang Baek Ho,
of all people.

50
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:18,030
Baek Ho said he wanted to meet
with Director Ma.

51
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:20,160
Director Ma is supposed
to meet us here later.

52
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,270
- Perfect.
- What?

53
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:24,140
Seo Rin is coming here?

54
00:04:24,770 --> 00:04:26,270
- Why?
- Excuse me?

55
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,370
I asked Jin Hong Ju to set up
a meeting with her.

56
00:04:28,710 --> 00:04:30,380
I have some things to ask her
about the accident.

57
00:04:43,250 --> 00:04:45,060
Why isn't she picking up?

58
00:04:46,290 --> 00:04:50,190
The person you're calling is unavailable.
Connecting to voicemail.

59
00:04:55,070 --> 00:04:56,170
Listen, Lawyer Kang.

60
00:04:56,770 --> 00:04:59,570
I understand you care about Oh Jang Mi,

61
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:03,140
but Seo Rin still hasn't fully recovered.

62
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:06,010
So why do you insist on bringing up
the car accident?

63
00:05:06,610 --> 00:05:08,380
Have you considered the trauma
it might cause her?

64
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:12,120
- I'm sorry?
- She hasn't made a full recovery,

65
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:15,250
so I would ask that you refrain
from contacting my daughter...

66
00:05:15,550 --> 00:05:17,160
like this in the future.

67
00:05:24,130 --> 00:05:25,660
She was talking about her daughter
as if she were a little child.

68
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,800
But is it really something
to be so sensitive about?

69
00:05:29,570 --> 00:05:32,000
I know, right? I'm sorry, Baek Ho.

70
00:05:32,940 --> 00:05:35,240
No, I'm the one who's sorry
for asking a difficult favor.

71
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:43,480
Now it will look like
a completely natural mole.

72
00:05:44,250 --> 00:05:45,250
Why don't you take a look?

73
00:05:56,890 --> 00:05:59,500
Now it looks exactly the same.

74
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,410
Seo Rin.

75
00:06:07,710 --> 00:06:09,940
What? What's going on?

76
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:14,010
Seo Rin, why weren't you
answering my calls?

77
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:16,110
I thought you had plans with Hong Ju.

78
00:06:16,410 --> 00:06:17,420
That's right.

79
00:06:17,850 --> 00:06:20,620
Team Leader Jin kept pestering me
to treat her to a meal,

80
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:23,760
- so I made plans and completely forgot.
- Treat her to a meal?

81
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:28,030
Oh, my. It sounds like my Hong Ju
must have done you a huge favor.

82
00:06:28,990 --> 00:06:30,430
It's not like that.

83
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:34,230
Team Leader Jin just loves
getting free meals, you know?

84
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:38,700
And about that blog post,
I had it taken down, Mom.

85
00:06:38,970 --> 00:06:41,440
What do you mean, a blog post?

86
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:44,280
Some nasty comments.

87
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,980
I mentioned that a few hate comments
were bothering me,

88
00:06:47,210 --> 00:06:50,580
so Seo Rin had them all removed.

89
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:53,520
Seo Rin, can we talk for a minute?

90
00:06:54,020 --> 00:06:55,020
Sure.

91
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:02,990
CEO Chae isn't someone
who would care about a few nasty comments.

92
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,900
So, what did you think of
General Manager Kang?

93
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:07,700
Still don't remember him?

94
00:07:08,670 --> 00:07:12,270
- I don't know.
- You used to follow him everywhere.

95
00:07:12,670 --> 00:07:13,670
I did?

96
00:07:13,940 --> 00:07:14,940
Of course you did.

97
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:18,480
You threw such a fit,
insisting you were going to marry him.

98
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,710
I see.

99
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:24,720
How could you not remember that?

100
00:07:25,250 --> 00:07:26,850
You've got something on you.

101
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:42,170
Don't waste your energy
on pointless things,

102
00:07:42,570 --> 00:07:44,200
and learn as much as you can
from General Manager Kang.

103
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:48,710
- You absolutely need him by your side.
- Okay.

104
00:07:49,340 --> 00:07:51,340
Can I go to my room now?

105
00:08:01,650 --> 00:08:04,320
Baek Ho said he wanted to meet
with Director Ma.

106
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:06,620
Director Ma is supposed
to meet us here later.

107
00:08:06,620 --> 00:08:07,630
Perfect.

108
00:08:11,230 --> 00:08:12,530
So this was all Jin Hong Ju's doing.

109
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:17,400
Jin Hong Ju is the only one who can
enter my office without raising suspicion.

110
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:21,870
How dare she tell Seo Rin to come
to Oh Jang Mi's hospital room?

111
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:24,380
And in front of Lawyer Kang Baek Ho,
of all people.

112
00:08:25,410 --> 00:08:26,410
Jin Hong Ju.

113
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:29,050
You have to be the one behind this.

114
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:32,480
What exactly do you know?

115
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:43,160
Manager Lee, tail Jin Hong Ju for me.

116
00:08:43,730 --> 00:08:47,270
I'm certain Jin Hong Ju
is behind this whole thing.

117
00:08:48,130 --> 00:08:51,240
Find out what she knows
and her plans immediately.

118
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:01,850
- Why?
- Seo Rin,

119
00:09:01,850 --> 00:09:05,150
so what were these nasty comments
about CEO Chae on the blog...

120
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:06,780
that you had taken down?

121
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:09,490
Can you share the address for that blog
with me?

122
00:09:09,850 --> 00:09:13,820
- I'd rather not.
- Are you covering for your mother?

123
00:09:14,190 --> 00:09:15,360
This isn't something you should cover for.

124
00:09:17,060 --> 00:09:19,530
I have a right to know what she did wrong.

125
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:24,300
As an elder in this family,
I should discipline my daughter-in-law.

126
00:09:24,370 --> 00:09:26,900
You're going to run and tell Grandfather,
aren't you?

127
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:29,710
What? Do you think
I have such a big mouth?

128
00:09:29,770 --> 00:09:32,810
Yes, as light as a feather,
from what I hear.

129
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:34,610
Seriously, why you...

130
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:37,280
Oh my, were you just about to hit me?

131
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:40,150
I've got to tell Grandfather about this.

132
00:09:40,690 --> 00:09:41,820
No.

133
00:09:42,450 --> 00:09:45,420
How could I possibly hit you?

134
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:48,730
I was just stretching my arm.

135
00:09:50,060 --> 00:09:51,660
Anyway, forget it.

136
00:09:52,330 --> 00:09:56,670
- I'll just ask Hong Ju.
- Ask her what? Just drop it.

137
00:09:57,070 --> 00:09:58,940
My mom has been through enough today.

138
00:09:59,570 --> 00:10:00,940
If things get serious,

139
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:03,310
Chae Hwa Young might find that woman
from the fruit store...

140
00:10:03,310 --> 00:10:04,910
and trace everything back to me.

141
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,910
I'd better end it here.

142
00:10:21,860 --> 00:10:23,430
That's my girl.

143
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,360
Seeing how she took my side,

144
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:29,270
it makes raising her as my daughter
feel worthwhile.

145
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:12,880
Hwa Young.

146
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:14,850
Is something wrong?

147
00:11:15,250 --> 00:11:18,480
Nothing.
It's just been a really rough day.

148
00:11:19,850 --> 00:11:22,120
I feel like I won't make it
if I don't have a drink.

149
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:24,920
Even so, don't drink too much.

150
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:27,490
Drinking on a rough day like this
will take a toll on you.

151
00:11:27,490 --> 00:11:28,530
Let go.

152
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:35,630
Hwa Young, just get it all off your chest.

153
00:11:36,230 --> 00:11:38,570
Tell me everything...

154
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:40,870
if that puts your mind at ease.

155
00:11:41,510 --> 00:11:43,440
No, I can't tell you.

156
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:46,640
If I were to bare my soul to you,

157
00:11:47,850 --> 00:11:49,850
you'd see me differently, Nam Bong.

158
00:11:50,250 --> 00:11:51,280
That's not true.

159
00:11:51,950 --> 00:11:53,350
Because I'm on your side.

160
00:11:55,950 --> 00:11:58,820
Knowing you went through that ordeal
because of me,

161
00:11:59,820 --> 00:12:01,230
I feel terrible.

162
00:12:01,590 --> 00:12:03,160
It wasn't your fault,

163
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:05,030
so please don't worry about it.

164
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,080
I'm sorry.

165
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:23,150
You'll get through this.

166
00:12:35,390 --> 00:12:36,460
Dad.

167
00:12:37,060 --> 00:12:38,700
If this is what you get
for being a good person,

168
00:12:39,230 --> 00:12:41,130
who would want to live a life like yours?

169
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:43,670
Who would want to live like Jang Mi?

170
00:12:52,010 --> 00:12:53,210
(Professor Kang Nam Bong is
having an affair with CEO Chae Hwa Young.)

171
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:54,350
(Do not trust Chae Hwa Young.)

172
00:12:54,810 --> 00:12:56,850
Wait, what is this?

173
00:12:57,920 --> 00:13:01,190
Professor Kang is having an affair
with CEO Chae?

174
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:06,190
Who would send something like this?

175
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:09,590
Professor Kang Nam Bong is
having an affair with CEO Chae Hwa Young.

176
00:13:09,590 --> 00:13:11,000
Do not trust Chae Hwa Young.

177
00:13:11,230 --> 00:13:13,230
Out of the blue, a text telling me
not to trust CEO Chae.

178
00:13:13,830 --> 00:13:15,000
What's this all about?

179
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:19,800
Wait. Professor Kang Nam Bong
is Baek Ho's father.

180
00:13:21,140 --> 00:13:25,640
Tae Pyung, Tok Hee can't sleep.

181
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:29,880
Mom.

182
00:13:30,810 --> 00:13:31,920
Should I tell Baek Ho...

183
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:35,050
about this bad news,
or should I keep it to myself?

184
00:13:37,050 --> 00:13:38,890
Tok Hee is sick.

185
00:13:40,290 --> 00:13:42,060
I miss Jang Mi.

186
00:13:42,590 --> 00:13:44,200
Jang Mi is gone.

187
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:52,800
(Director Ma Seo Rin)

188
00:14:03,610 --> 00:14:04,620
Tae Pyung.

189
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:06,920
You shouldn't trust
Chae Hwa Young anymore.

190
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:09,950
I feel bad for Baek Ho,

191
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:11,720
but the same goes
for Professor Kang Nam Bong,

192
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:13,360
who's responsible for our dad's death.

193
00:14:14,020 --> 00:14:15,860
We can never see our dad again,

194
00:14:16,430 --> 00:14:18,500
but Professor Kang
hasn't paid for his crime at all.

195
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:20,830
The fact that he gets to go on
laughing and eating...

196
00:14:21,400 --> 00:14:22,400
just makes me furious.

197
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,610
Here you are, sir.

198
00:14:27,940 --> 00:14:31,580
- Are these the papers?
- Yes, sir.

199
00:14:31,580 --> 00:14:32,580
(Deed of Gift for a Building)

200
00:14:32,580 --> 00:14:33,910
By tomorrow morning,

201
00:14:34,310 --> 00:14:36,750
- make sure it gets registered.
- Yes, sir. I'll take care of it.

202
00:14:38,850 --> 00:14:40,020
I wonder if she'll be happy to receive it.

203
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:41,820
I'm sure she'll be thrilled.

204
00:14:42,990 --> 00:14:43,990
Registration?

205
00:14:44,990 --> 00:14:45,990
Could it be...

206
00:14:46,620 --> 00:14:48,530
Right. Once the registration is finalized,

207
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:51,130
I'm going to announce it at dinner
when everyone's there.

208
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:54,930
I have to make things crystal clear
to end all the gossip.

209
00:14:54,930 --> 00:14:57,070
I'll ensure everyone keeps quiet, sir.

210
00:15:02,640 --> 00:15:04,210
You seem to be in a good mood,
Team Leader Jin.

211
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:07,480
Because my love life is going very well.

212
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:09,480
I see.

213
00:15:09,680 --> 00:15:12,880
You mean the one you mentioned last time?
The guy you said was your ideal type?

214
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,620
So, who's the lucky guy?

215
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:17,590
A warm-hearted man
who's the complete opposite of you.

216
00:15:18,860 --> 00:15:23,030
- The complete opposite of me?
- You have this cold, icy side to you.

217
00:15:23,430 --> 00:15:25,230
Of course, I respect you,

218
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:27,160
but as a romantic partner,

219
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:28,830
you're too cold,
and I don't want to be in your arms.

220
00:15:29,230 --> 00:15:30,470
You think I would want to hold you
in my arms?

221
00:15:31,940 --> 00:15:34,040
I guess that's why we've been able
to last this long.

222
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:36,770
Because we're colleagues, not lovers.

223
00:15:36,770 --> 00:15:40,780
So who melted your frozen heart?

224
00:15:40,780 --> 00:15:42,110
Are you curious?

225
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:46,280
How about a double date with Seo Rin?
The four of us. Are you in?

226
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:49,220
Why are you randomly bringing Director Ma
into this?

227
00:15:49,420 --> 00:15:53,390
Director Ma has been a lot more docile
since her accident.

228
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:55,960
Besides, CEO Chae looks at you
like you're her son-in-law.

229
00:15:56,290 --> 00:15:59,030
- Come on, be nicer to her.
- I'm not interested.

230
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:09,970
- What now?
- Hong Ju, it's finally happening.

231
00:16:10,070 --> 00:16:11,340
What do you mean, "it's happening?"

232
00:16:11,410 --> 00:16:14,980
I eavesdropped when Secretary Kim
brought in some documents to be signed.

233
00:16:14,980 --> 00:16:16,010
And?

234
00:16:16,010 --> 00:16:19,980
The Chairman told him
to have the registration finished...

235
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,850
by tomorrow.

236
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:23,120
Registration?

237
00:16:23,890 --> 00:16:27,390
Is Father really going to give us
some of his shares?

238
00:16:27,490 --> 00:16:28,830
That's right.

239
00:16:29,030 --> 00:16:30,190
"Once the registration is finalized,"

240
00:16:30,490 --> 00:16:32,460
"I'm going to announce it at dinner
when everyone's there."

241
00:16:33,060 --> 00:16:35,570
"I have to make things crystal clear
to end all the gossip."

242
00:16:37,230 --> 00:16:40,000
- That's exactly what he said.
- Oh my gosh.

243
00:16:40,570 --> 00:16:43,440
- It's really happening.
- Right?

244
00:16:43,640 --> 00:16:45,980
Mom, your wish is finally coming true.

245
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:48,010
I'm so excited.

246
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:49,950
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

247
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,390
The Chairman...

248
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:56,320
I mean, my father...

249
00:16:57,090 --> 00:17:00,520
is finally transferring some of his shares
to my mother and me.

250
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:04,190
(Professor Kang Nam Bong is
having an affair with CEO Chae Hwa Young.)

251
00:17:04,260 --> 00:17:05,360
(Do not trust Chae Hwa Young.)

252
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,860
So that's what's going on.

253
00:17:08,370 --> 00:17:10,330
But "Do not trust Chae Hwa Young?"

254
00:17:10,500 --> 00:17:11,770
What does that mean?

255
00:17:12,070 --> 00:17:13,470
What do you mean,
"Do not trust Chae Hwa Young?"

256
00:17:14,300 --> 00:17:17,240
Chae Hwa Young is a thief.
She's a bad person.

257
00:17:17,740 --> 00:17:19,880
That's right. Mom, you're so pure,

258
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,910
- so you say it like it is.
- Right.

259
00:17:22,810 --> 00:17:27,620
- I wonder if Mom is right.
- Tae Pyung is the best. You're handsome.

260
00:17:28,190 --> 00:17:31,860
- Jang Mi is pretty.
- Grandma, what about me? Aren't I pretty?

261
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:34,930
Of course, Bo Ra is pretty.
You're adorable.

262
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:36,230
You're so pretty, Bo Ra.

263
00:17:36,690 --> 00:17:39,160
You're pretty too, Grandma. And cute!

264
00:17:41,730 --> 00:17:43,070
I said, what are you talking about?

265
00:17:43,570 --> 00:17:46,670
- Who told you not to trust CEO Chae?
- I don't know either.

266
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:48,940
Anyway, just stay out of it for now,
Tae Sook.

267
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:52,710
You keep talking in riddles.

268
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:54,210
Because I'm just as confused as you are.

269
00:17:57,820 --> 00:18:01,450
Yes, thank you. I'll see you then.

270
00:18:04,690 --> 00:18:06,160
So, did we secure the event?

271
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:07,890
You bet. Who do you think I am?

272
00:18:08,260 --> 00:18:10,760
The launch of the new high-end watch brand
absolutely has to be...

273
00:18:10,760 --> 00:18:12,260
at our hotel.

274
00:18:12,330 --> 00:18:16,870
- You know that, right?
- Yes. Since CEO Yamamoto respects you,

275
00:18:17,130 --> 00:18:18,370
I'd say we have a good chance.

276
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:20,670
If this deal goes through,

277
00:18:20,670 --> 00:18:22,770
our lackluster results
from last quarter...

278
00:18:22,870 --> 00:18:25,780
- will be completely turned around.
- I'll prepare the paperwork.

279
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:28,110
Good. The meeting's
at ten o'clock tomorrow.

280
00:18:28,950 --> 00:18:31,420
We've done all the legwork
and this is practically in the bag,

281
00:18:31,650 --> 00:18:34,250
but they're a watch company,
so we absolutely must be on time.

282
00:18:34,620 --> 00:18:37,720
And don't take it lightly
when they say being late is a dealbreaker.

283
00:18:37,860 --> 00:18:39,020
I've taken it to heart.

284
00:18:40,890 --> 00:18:42,790
Excellent.

285
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:45,400
This event is as good as ours.

286
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:47,560
I'm going to land this contract,
no matter what.

287
00:18:53,370 --> 00:18:54,770
A divorce trial?

288
00:18:55,510 --> 00:18:56,510
Yes.

289
00:18:56,970 --> 00:19:00,480
The husband used work as an excuse
to have an affair with a client,

290
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,010
but his wife is very sharp.

291
00:19:02,450 --> 00:19:05,350
- And she gathered airtight evidence.
- Then...

292
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:07,450
you're going to win the case.

293
00:19:08,690 --> 00:19:11,420
Of course. I don't take cases I can't win.

294
00:19:11,820 --> 00:19:14,660
And I'm definitely going
to win today's trial too.

295
00:19:14,730 --> 00:19:17,260
So just have the champagne ready.

296
00:19:18,060 --> 00:19:20,600
Right. Of course, you'll win.

297
00:19:21,830 --> 00:19:24,300
- Here.
- Let me see.

298
00:19:27,770 --> 00:19:29,240
My handsome husband.

299
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:31,410
I'm heading out.

300
00:19:31,480 --> 00:19:32,480
Right.

301
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:35,010
You must be bored
since your lecture is off today.

302
00:19:35,010 --> 00:19:36,480
Why don't you watch a movie?

303
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:49,560
(To Professor Kang Nam Bong)

304
00:19:50,990 --> 00:19:52,000
What's this?

305
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:59,270
What is this?

306
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:01,510
What is it?

307
00:20:02,470 --> 00:20:03,640
It's for you.

308
00:20:04,840 --> 00:20:07,980
- What could it be?
- Go on, open it. I'm curious.

309
00:20:18,490 --> 00:20:19,520
What is it?

310
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:21,060
It's nothing.

311
00:20:21,660 --> 00:20:22,990
What is it? Let me see.

312
00:20:23,490 --> 00:20:26,730
It's nothing important.
It's just an assignment from a student.

313
00:20:27,530 --> 00:20:30,130
This kid never turned in assignments
on time...

314
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:32,970
and is now going all out for the grade.

315
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:36,240
- What?
- Didn't you say you were running late?

316
00:20:36,510 --> 00:20:38,740
- Aren't you leaving?
- Right.

317
00:20:39,140 --> 00:20:40,740
- I'll be back.
- Okay.

318
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:43,410
- Good luck.
- Okay.

319
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:00,960
"Kang Nam Bong."

320
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:05,470
"Next time, I'll send this to your wife,
Lawyer Han Young Ja."

321
00:21:06,570 --> 00:21:08,010
Who on earth would...

322
00:21:08,740 --> 00:21:10,170
Who could it be?

323
00:21:11,140 --> 00:21:12,380
Here.

324
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:18,880
Make it pretty.

325
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:23,790
Mom, you can't just make a mess like this.

326
00:21:24,150 --> 00:21:26,790
Bo Ra, didn't I tell you not to do this?

327
00:21:26,890 --> 00:21:30,030
- My uncle did it.
- Your uncle?

328
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,070
Are you back from a delivery?

329
00:21:39,900 --> 00:21:41,640
I thought I was going
to have a heart attack.

330
00:21:42,870 --> 00:21:46,180
Tae Pyung's helmet is so cool.
I want to wear it too.

331
00:21:46,710 --> 00:21:47,710
A heart attack?

332
00:21:48,210 --> 00:21:49,450
What kind of trouble did you get into?

333
00:21:49,580 --> 00:21:52,980
Bad people shouldn't get
to live happily ever after, you know?

334
00:21:53,050 --> 00:21:54,180
What are you talking about?

335
00:21:54,690 --> 00:21:56,390
What kind of trouble
have you been getting into?

336
00:21:56,450 --> 00:21:59,160
Just you wait.
I'll tell you everything soon enough.

337
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:02,560
Our dad died in such an unfair way,

338
00:22:03,130 --> 00:22:04,800
so I have to make them pay,
at least a little.

339
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:12,240
Darn it.

340
00:22:15,770 --> 00:22:17,540
Should I tell Hwa Young about this?

341
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:20,110
I should.

342
00:22:35,390 --> 00:22:38,130
Professor Kang,
I'm a little busy right now.

343
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:40,630
I received strange photos.

344
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:44,600
- What was that again?
- It's photos of us. It said...

345
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:47,740
they're going to send them
to my wife next time.

346
00:22:49,470 --> 00:22:52,080
And you have no idea who sent the photos?

347
00:22:52,780 --> 00:22:57,150
I don't know. A courier in a helmet
delivered a yellow envelope...

348
00:22:58,010 --> 00:23:01,020
with photos of us at the wine bar
and a letter.

349
00:23:02,650 --> 00:23:03,790
A yellow envelope?

350
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:05,760
All right.

351
00:23:06,660 --> 00:23:09,460
Don't say a word to anyone
and just sit tight.

352
00:23:09,760 --> 00:23:11,460
I'll find out who's behind this.

353
00:23:16,630 --> 00:23:17,830
Manager Lee, come in.

354
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:26,580
Is something wrong?

355
00:23:27,110 --> 00:23:30,380
It's just one thing after another.
I can't catch a break.

356
00:23:30,750 --> 00:23:33,880
- Sorry?
- Professor Kang was sent photos.

357
00:23:34,180 --> 00:23:35,290
It has to be Jin Hong Ju.

358
00:23:35,850 --> 00:23:38,420
I think she is stirring up trouble again.

359
00:23:39,260 --> 00:23:41,490
It's the same trick Yeom San Wol pulled,
you know?

360
00:23:44,590 --> 00:23:46,030
Why are you so quiet?

361
00:23:46,030 --> 00:23:49,270
Have you been seeing Professor Kang again?

362
00:23:49,330 --> 00:23:52,500
Manager Lee,
that is not what's important right now.

363
00:23:52,870 --> 00:23:55,540
If Lawyer Han Young Ja
finds out about this,

364
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:58,840
the wedding between Jun Ho
and Seo Rin will be off.

365
00:24:00,440 --> 00:24:02,010
Check on what Jin Hong Ju is up to, now.

366
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:10,790
Baek Ho.

367
00:24:11,190 --> 00:24:14,390
I went to all this trouble to bring it.
At least have one, please.

368
00:24:15,060 --> 00:24:16,130
No, thank you.

369
00:24:17,190 --> 00:24:18,960
You have no interest in me at all.

370
00:24:19,430 --> 00:24:21,730
You were only interested in Oh Jang Mi,
weren't you?

371
00:24:21,870 --> 00:24:23,730
I'm just really busy right now.

372
00:24:25,300 --> 00:24:27,640
Just because CEO Chae told you
not to see Director Ma,

373
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:30,470
how could your attitude toward me
change so completely?

374
00:24:30,810 --> 00:24:32,540
My hands are tied.

375
00:24:32,940 --> 00:24:37,150
You heard what CEO Chae said.
Seo Rin hasn't fully recovered yet,

376
00:24:37,480 --> 00:24:39,420
and she said you shouldn't meet
because it might confuse her.

377
00:24:40,220 --> 00:24:41,220
I see.

378
00:24:45,560 --> 00:24:48,590
Jin Hong Ju was in Kang Baek Ho's office.
She just left.

379
00:24:48,890 --> 00:24:52,000
- So, nothing else to report?
- That's right.

380
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:54,700
Jin Hong Ju may be intentionally
creating a smokescreen.

381
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:57,770
I'll have to interrogate her
when she gets back.

382
00:24:58,700 --> 00:25:00,740
Are the documents
for tomorrow's meeting ready?

383
00:25:01,670 --> 00:25:03,440
Leave them on my desk.

384
00:25:06,140 --> 00:25:07,140
Really?

385
00:25:08,910 --> 00:25:11,550
If we can just land that launch event
for our hotel,

386
00:25:11,850 --> 00:25:15,850
it'll be a huge boost for our group.
A win that big is what we need.

387
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:18,460
Yes. Our sales have been slow,

388
00:25:18,690 --> 00:25:20,960
but I'll be sure to make up for it
with this.

389
00:25:21,660 --> 00:25:25,600
Yamamoto is very punctual,
so you'd better be on top of your game.

390
00:25:25,830 --> 00:25:26,960
I'm aware.

391
00:25:27,460 --> 00:25:31,130
All the necessary documents are ready,
and the meeting is set for tomorrow,

392
00:25:31,230 --> 00:25:32,700
so I'll make sure there are no mistakes.

393
00:25:34,070 --> 00:25:36,240
Mom, what time is your meeting tomorrow?

394
00:25:36,610 --> 00:25:41,140
If it's an important one, I can pick out
an outfit and shoes for you.

395
00:25:41,510 --> 00:25:42,550
You'd do that?

396
00:25:44,250 --> 00:25:46,980
I think
Seo Rin is finally starting to mature.

397
00:25:47,550 --> 00:25:49,790
We just need her memory
to come back fully.

398
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:51,860
I hear Director Kim...

399
00:25:51,860 --> 00:25:55,360
is bringing over a famous neurologist,
Dr. Kim, from the US.

400
00:25:55,730 --> 00:25:57,160
Just hang in there, Seo Rin.

401
00:25:58,460 --> 00:25:59,660
Yes, Grandfather.

402
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:05,140
Chae Hwa Young, just you wait.

403
00:26:05,770 --> 00:26:07,700
Once I find some undeniable proof,

404
00:26:08,140 --> 00:26:10,840
the first thing I'll do is expose
all your evil deeds to Grandfather.

405
00:26:23,150 --> 00:26:24,320
Jin Hong Ju.

406
00:26:24,320 --> 00:26:25,390
Give me your phone.

407
00:26:25,860 --> 00:26:26,860
Ma'am.

408
00:26:27,690 --> 00:26:28,830
What are you talking about?

409
00:26:28,990 --> 00:26:31,730
Do you think I don't know
what you've been up to?

410
00:26:32,260 --> 00:26:34,160
Do you have any idea how many times
I've let this slide?

411
00:26:34,430 --> 00:26:36,870
Ma'am, what's all this about?

412
00:26:37,470 --> 00:26:39,600
I have something important tomorrow,

413
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:42,270
so today I'm just giving you
one last warning.

414
00:26:42,610 --> 00:26:44,870
If you pull any more dirty tricks
behind my back,

415
00:26:45,110 --> 00:26:47,940
you and your mother will pay the price.

416
00:26:48,080 --> 00:26:50,950
I don't know what you're talking about.

417
00:26:51,210 --> 00:26:53,820
- I feel really wronged.
- Really?

418
00:26:54,450 --> 00:26:58,150
We'll see if you're still saying that
when I catch you red-handed.

419
00:27:07,260 --> 00:27:08,430
What was that all about?

420
00:27:37,390 --> 00:27:39,830
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

421
00:27:41,600 --> 00:27:43,870
(Confidential,
Global Brand "P" Launch Event)

422
00:27:47,900 --> 00:27:49,940
(Final Proposal and Future Schedule)

423
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:55,880
(From: Dream Hotel
Planning and Marketing TF)

424
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:57,010
(To: CEO Yamamoto, P Company)

425
00:28:06,060 --> 00:28:07,060
Chae Hwa Young.

426
00:28:07,660 --> 00:28:09,860
I'm going to throw a wrench
in all your plans.

427
00:28:10,960 --> 00:28:12,560
Until the pain is so unbearable
that you wish you were dead.

428
00:28:13,260 --> 00:28:15,630
I'm going to crush you
every single chance I get.

429
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:37,090
(The First Man)

430
00:28:37,120 --> 00:28:40,390
Director Ma and Jang Mi must have been
in that accident together.

431
00:28:40,890 --> 00:28:43,590
If I meet with Director Ma,
I should be able to find out for sure.

432
00:28:43,730 --> 00:28:47,760
Chae Hwa Young, you'll wish for death.
This is just a taste of what's to come.

433
00:28:47,930 --> 00:28:50,400
You're in for a world of pain,
so you'd better look forward to it.

434
00:28:50,570 --> 00:28:53,500
No excuses.
I will not tolerate this mistake!

435
00:28:53,800 --> 00:28:57,040
This is more than a pay cut.
You're forfeiting three months' salary.

436
00:28:57,110 --> 00:28:58,110
Mark my words.

437
00:28:59,140 --> 00:29:01,080
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
